data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to see this beautiful home, located just minutes from the Castle Rock Factory Outlet Mall and Downtown Castle Rock! This gorgeous 4-bedroom house has a huge kitchen fully equipped with an island and tons of storage space and a massive primary bedroom with a fireplace and office or reading nook. The finished basement is perfect for a houseguest and includes a media room, bedroom, and bathroom! The enormous fenced in backyard is the picture-perfect place for entertaining with its large deck, firepit, built in garden beds and well cared for lawn. This beauty won’t last long!
